{"id": 1600, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，你厌倦什么样的饭局话题？", "description": "要么庸俗，要么无解，讨论起来令人身心疲倦的饭局话题。", "record_count": 7226, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201703311754480mGdHFefEJi2nM98.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-02T17:00:59Z", "options": [{"id": 186880, "content": "下次吃啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 514176}, {"id": 187136, "content": "相亲，结婚，买房，生孩子，外带呲牛逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991775}, {"id": 188672, "content": "一起去同学家玩，大家以及长辈都再说未来工作规划，以做什么赚钱和女孩子一定要找稳定的工作。（其实这没什么错的，只是和我的想法多少有点出入）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659826}, {"id": 189952, "content": "你老婆最近怎么样？", "image": "img/option/option/20170409131532RN2FY8Toguxjbdp7", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981981}, {"id": 186881, "content": "到底要说什么话题才能满足你们这些人？", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960084}, {"id": 187137, "content": "天知道你管我的理想是何居心", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988362}, {"id": 188161, "content": "拿你和饭桌上的其他人做比较！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993746}, {"id": 188417, "content": "房子买哪儿啦，什么时候生小孩啊，小孩要不要送私校啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581266}, {"id": 196097, "content": "敬酒！既然说了是饭局好好吃饭不行吗！吃一个就敬个酒 你良心过得去嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013373}, {"id": 186882, "content": "房子", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715498}, {"id": 187138, "content": "一堆喝酒吹牛逼的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984980}, {"id": 187394, "content": "对聚众吃饭厌恶至极。包括家里，外面的各类聚餐。。。。。。为减少污染，讲究卫生，改善民生，政府应该提倡限制每桌吃饭人数，并为其制定法规。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656406}, {"id": 186883, "content": "寒暄之后都在低头玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991266}, {"id": 187651, "content": "谈恋爱没", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928052}, {"id": 186884, "content": "抓着我疯狂地进行思想教育，不仔细听我讲话就把我当傻子，对我进行社会经验的教育。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991265}, {"id": 187140, "content": "喝完酒以后，就开始bbbb，没完没了...", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991786}, {"id": 188676, "content": "你工资多少钱，有男／女朋友吗，慢热你有一个月挣多少钱……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956251}, {"id": 189444, "content": "倒逼自己有多忙，貌似日进斗金的新一代土豪，鬼知道你天天闲的除了撸剧就是刷朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997368}, {"id": 189956, "content": "跟爸妈的老朋友及其亲属欢聚一堂共进晚餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871628}, {"id": 186885, "content": "不知道为什么 和大人在一起的饭局 总是喜欢不起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942716}, {"id": 188421, "content": "我遇见最奇葩的一个，远房亲戚。张口闭口还要我继承他的思想，传承他的人脉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 975984}, {"id": 188677, "content": "上条写错了：你男朋友每月挣多少钱……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956251}, {"id": 187142, "content": "其实大部分情况下，话题的发起者只想知道你过得不好，然后给你他们的人生经验，实现自我价值实现，提高自己的自我满足感，秀了见识，共享了经验，还帮了人。当然有部分人，只是单纯的想知道你过得不好，然后同情你一把", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991794}, {"id": 188166, "content": "对话没营养的饭局", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993735}, {"id": 186887, "content": "他和她居然在一起了！他和她还没分呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936310}, {"id": 187143, "content": "车子，房子，孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991807}, {"id": 187911, "content": "我买了哪个牌子的哪款包包 谁谁谁新出的鞋子我穿脚上了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993355}, {"id": 186888, "content": "他和她居然在一起了！他和她还没分呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936310}, {"id": 187912, "content": "强行价值观输出  好为人师", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743334}, {"id": 188168, "content": "就想一个人或者一家人吃。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993757}, {"id": 189192, "content": "从来不见\n找你托关系\n找你借钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 961332}, {"id": 188425, "content": "爱情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920901}, {"id": 204298, "content": "讲述我失恋的全过程", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031657}, {"id": 187146, "content": "装B", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562166}, {"id": 188170, "content": "拿你和餐桌上的同龄人做比较！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993746}, {"id": 187147, "content": "所以到底什么话题可以让你们开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889364}, {"id": 187403, "content": "就不能安心吃饭吗说什么话……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991523}, {"id": 188171, "content": "是饭局就讨厌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936279}, {"id": 188427, "content": "\"呀你可好啦，现在人赢一个！我找工作/出国/考研/XX各种不顺……\"言语里透着各种酸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967513}, {"id": 189963, "content": "认识某个富二代或者认识哪个牛逼朋友~每次都要说一遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988726}, {"id": 186892, "content": "你啥时候才能找着对象呀。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525605}, {"id": 187405, "content": "陪领导吃饭，领导挺矜持。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992650}, {"id": 187661, "content": "娃的成绩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992993}, {"id": 186895, "content": "最讨厌敬酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902112}, {"id": 187151, "content": "自我介绍，各种喝酒的游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 837887}, {"id": 188687, "content": "工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995117}, {"id": 186896, "content": "房子车子票子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786145}, {"id": 193552, "content": "来来回回只会酒桌上装逼的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1005103}, {"id": 187409, "content": "单纯回忆过去", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922915}, {"id": 187921, "content": "为什么不找男友呀，为什么不结婚呀，为什么不生小孩呀，为什么不买房呀。。。关你屁事呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993373}]}